---
title: Pork Risotto Casserole with Kale, Tomato, and Parmesan
description: Risotto usually involves a lot of time carefully watching and stirring a pan full of simmering rice, but our chefs found a casserole workaround that makes it a cinch. After giving the meat, rice, and veggies a quick toss in a large pan, the whole thing is sprinkled with cheese and transferred to the oven, where it bakes its way to creamy, al dente perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-risotto-casserole-8bc11def.jpg
